{"tid":1716533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港情勢緊張 政府協調華航今晚載回中大81名台生","createTime":"2019-11-13T11:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:11:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5da0db326fe0613d9ec5febc480a31cf967b6ae2","tid":1716533,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"〔記者吳柏軒／台北報導〕香港反送中局勢演變，讓大學校園也淪為示威者與警方的戰場，教育部表示，經駐港人員與香港中文大學的台灣學生會接洽，目前已協調出1班華航班機，將載運81名港中大台生回來，另有41名台生也自行購票返台，其他學校也將持續關注並提供必要協助。<br />\n<br />\n教育部表示，在香港的台灣留學生（含交換生等）共有1021人，而在香港中文大學則有約303人左右，因香港局勢惡化，經駐港教育人員上午緊急聯繫，目前在港台生都通報平安，但已有台生要求回台。"},{"pid":"3e28e04ef64a18f923a4925d42f19c787dd8174e","tid":1716533,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2976676?fbclid=IwAR0KSMtfp18DKhAfehLhtZd1yrWNn_n4pqZ5f3DLh-vYxs55QLEGO_v7fcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2976676%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0KSMtfp18DKhAfehLhtZd1yrWNn_n4pqZ5f3DLh-vYxs55QLEGO_v7fcw&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=0f3a81b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2976676%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0KSMtfp18DKhAfehLhtZd1yrWNn_n4pqZ5f3DLh-vYxs55QLEGO_v7fcw&h=865c2e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2976676?fbclid=IwAR0KSMtfp18DKhAfehLhtZd1yrWNn_n4pqZ5f3DLh-vYxs55QLEGO_v7fcw</a>"},{"pid":"cf08cd943b71ba1f01e871bc63a2602aa4bf818a","tid":1716533,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"Twitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=ee11342c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><b